node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 26, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'What's keeping you? The only thing that should keep you in a relationship is pure love. Don't let fear keep you. Don't let low self-esteem keep you. If you're not getting the love you deserve, make moves!! G'.

Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You have to love yourself enough to set a standard for your life that you're unwilling to compromise. If you accept the standards of others for your life you'll never be happy. TONYBRFEIRE @TONYGASKINS'.

Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Separation before elevation. You have to let some people and things go so you can go to the next level.'.

node.text: It’s been a blessing witnessing Championship Culture over the last couple of years with Coach Drew @baylormbb and the crew! Looking forward to working with the team this week! #Year3

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Thank God for the struggle, just as you would thank him for the success. The struggle is only intended to strengthen you. Let it make you not break you. A blessing is on the other side of this.'.
Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 10, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'True love gives you peace! It doesn't consume you with anxiety, that's lust! @TONYGASKIN'.
Photo by Tony Gaskins on July 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'It's time to face the mirror. Then do something with the truth that's revealed. G @TONYGASKINS S'.
